    <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">K-Electric Bill Online Check — Karachi 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">K-Electric (KE) is the sole electricity provider for Karachi and surrounding areas including Hub, Dhabeji, and Gharo. Unlike WAPDA DISCOs, K-Electric operates independently and uses a 13-digit account number instead of PITC's 14-digit reference number.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">How to check K-Electric bill online?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">Go to pakistanbill.online/k-electric-bill/ and enter your 13-digit K-Electric account number. Your Karachi electricity bill loads instantly — free, no login, no app needed.</div></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Where is K-Electric account number on bill?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">Your K-Electric account number is a 13-digit number printed at the top of your KE bill, labeled Account No. or Consumer Account No. It is different from WAPDA DISCOs which use a 14-digit reference number.</div></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">How to pay K-Electric bill online?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">Pay K-Electric bill through JazzCash (select Utility Bills → Electricity → K-Electric → enter 13-digit account number), EasyPaisa, HBL Mobile Banking, or any major bank app. You can also pay at K-Electric payment centers, One Bill counters, or franchise outlets across Karachi.</div></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Does K-Electric cover all of Karachi?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">K-Electric covers Karachi, Hub (Balochistan), Dhabeji, and Gharo. Areas like Karachi Cantt may have partial overlap. All other Pakistani cities are served by WAPDA DISCOs (LESCO, MEPCO, GEPCO, etc.).</div></details>
